name: I WAS THERE WHEN HIC ET NUNC MADE IT HAPPEN
description: Commemorative floppy disk to celebrate #NFTsForAll #WorldArtDay2021. There are many meanings behind it, you'll find hints in the tags. The main thing I wanted to create was a token for the memories of the first days on HIC ET NUNC, which allowed me to advance my artistic career one step further. Made by @Flyhohr
